    "The literature on IAEA regulations reflects the history of international efforts for nuclear safety and security.",
    "These works explore how standards and procedures established by the IAEA have developed and influenced the use and management of nuclear technology.",
    "This review provides a comprehensive understanding of how the IAEA's policies and frameworks have evolved over time, establishing foundations for insights applicable to AI technology regulation.",
